{
  "texts": [
    "Initially, we employed the QLoRA technique (Dettmers et al., 2023) for optimization.",
    "The QLoRA technique entails the following steps.",
    "First we quantized the models using 4-bit precision to reduce memory usage and computational requirements.",
    "The quantization process was facilitated by the BitsAndBytes library.",
    "Following quantization, we implemented the LoRA technique (Hu et al., 2021) using the PEFT library."
  ]
}